OL,7,FAn 'out of control' crisis in local
OL,8,Fgovernment funding can only be ended
OL,9,Fby the government providing billions
OL,10,Fof pounds more to councils, MPs have
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,FCouncils have repeatedly warned that
OL,14,Fmore than a decade of financial
OL,15,Fpressures exacerbated by rising demand
OL,16,Fand inflation are putting vital public
OL,17,Fservices under severe strain.
