OL,7,FA failure to increase allocations in
OL,8,Fthe local government finance
OL,9,Fsettlement to cover the shortfall
OL,10,Fwould push services including social
OL,11,Fcare and support for children with
OL,12,Fspecial educational needs to "breaking
OL,13,Fpoint", and could lead to well-run
OL,14,Fcouncils going effectively bust, the
OL,15,Fcommittee said.
