OL,7,FEarlier this month, Communities
OL,8,FSecretary Michael Gove increased the
OL,9,Flocal government financial settlement
OL,10,Ffor 2024/25 with measures worth an
OL,11,Fadditional #600 million, including
OL,12,F#500 million for adult and children's
OL,13,Fsocial care.
