OL,4,Cbillion black hole urge government to
OL,5,Chelp
OL,7,F"The government must use the local
OL,8,Fgovernment financial settlement to
OL,9,Fhelp bridge the #4 billion funding gap
OL,10,Ffor 2024-25 or risk already strained
OL,11,Fcouncil services becoming stretched to
OL,12,Fbreaking point.
OL,14,F"If the government fails to plug this
OL,15,Fgap, well-run councils could face the
OL,16,Fvery real prospect of effectively
OL,17,Fgoing bust."
