OL,7,FThe committee reiterated it would take
OL,8,F"billions of pounds a year" to put
OL,9,Fadult social care on a long-term
OL,10,Fsecure footing and called for
OL,11,Fwholesale reform of the way councils
OL,12,Fare financed.
OL,14,FIt said councils' core spending power,
OL,15,Fwhich is a combination of government
OL,16,Fgrants and the maximum that can be
OL,17,Fraised through council tax and
OL,18,Fbusiness rates, has not kept pace with
OL,19,Fgrowing pressures.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@[O]
