OL,7,FHowever, reductions in the funding
OL,8,Fprovided directly by the government
OL,9,Fhas led to councils relying
OL,10,Fincreasingly on revenue generated
OL,11,Flocally.
OL,13,FThe committee said council tax is
OL,14,F"regressive", in need of reform and
OL,15,Fhas a "disproportionately negative
OL,16,Fimpact on funding levels of local
OL,17,Fauthorities in the most deprived areas
OL,18,Fof the country".
