OL,7,FThe report highlighted that council
OL,8,Ftax charges are based on property
OL,9,Fvaluations from 1991.
OL,11,FWith prices rising considerably since
OL,12,Fthen, this means people occupying the
OL,13,Fmost valuable homes are paying less in
OL,14,Fcouncil tax as a proportion of their
OL,15,Fproperty's value than those living in
OL,16,Fthe least valuable properties, the
OL,17,Fcommittee said. There are also
OL,18,Fsignificant variations in the profile
OL,19,Fof properties in different areas.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G9/18
