OL,7,FThis means authorities in wealthier
OL,8,Fparts of the country can generate
OL,9,Fsignificantly more revenue than those
OL,10,Fin less well-off places with higher
OL,11,Flevels of demand for expensive
OL,12,Fservices, the report said.
