OL,7,FIt also said council tax thresholds
OL,8,Fshould be increased in line with
OL,9,Finflation. The committee described the
OL,10,Fbusiness rates system as "overly
OL,11,Fcomplex, outdated, and in need of
OL,12,Freform".
OL,14,FAs there is variation in the amount
OL,15,Fdifferent councils can generate
OL,16,Fthrough business rates, a formula is
OL,17,Fused to ensure some money is
OL,18,Fredistributed.
