OL,7,FHowever, this process uses a baseline
OL,8,Ffunding level calculated in 2013.
OL,9,FTherefore, the committee concludes,
OL,10,Fthe current process "does not account
OL,11,Ffor changes in population size,
OL,12,Fdemographics, and associated demand
OL,13,Ffor services in specific local
OL,14,Fauthorities".
OL,16,FMr Betts said: "Long-term reform is
OL,17,Fvitally needed. The funding model for
OL,18,Flocal councils is broken.
