OL,7,F"The business rates system is overly
OL,8,Fcomplex and in need of reform. Council
OL,9,Ftax is outdated and increasingly
OL,10,Fregressive.
OL,12,F"Councils being forced to hike up
OL,13,Fcouncil tax, in a forlorn attempt to
OL,14,Fplug increasingly large holes in their
OL,15,Fbudgets, is unsustainable and unfair
OL,16,Fto local people who are, year on year,
OL,17,Fseeing less services while paying
OL,18,Fmore."
